Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry. I will protect you during the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Do you have motion sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I'm venturing far away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a bit anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll travel much farther. Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Kingdom of Tristain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you living alone in that lonely place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is the work of fate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the vast world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, the other Void wielder...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected! Completely and utterly rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is your first time here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Henrietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the Queen lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting back, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad you have returned safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words are too kind for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm delighted that you are well too, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mark of Gandalfr...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have returned to being Louise's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's pretty inconvenient when you don't have a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, will you accept the title of chevalier this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is Tiffania, who we have been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, present yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tiffania.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am honoured to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my country, Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be weary from your long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot see your face clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to wear one in front of Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There's a reason for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been bothering me all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something on your head or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were an elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I wasn't planning to hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are disgusted by an elf, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you have your own story to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... actually... a half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deceased mother was an elf and the mistress of the Archduke of Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I lived secretly without being seen by anyone is because of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Archduke of Albion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not hate you for being an elf, Tiffania.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved Saito-san's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here in Tristain, I shall be your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I can show my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not have to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we have some tea over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything occur during the journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not wish to make you worry unnecessarily, so I did not report it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was some trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the woman from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one called Sheffield who attacked you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She threatened me and asked about\Nthe whereabouts of a second Void wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A second one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe the enemy knows something we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman, Sheffield, is quite skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to just ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's that skilled, her name must be known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could also become a rumour among the royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, be cautious from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall also look into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tread carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will accept the title of chevalier, will you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myoz...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myozunitonirun, I want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another wielder, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pawns have begun to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I do not dislike waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incompetent king has no choice but to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to find the other wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will find them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such kind words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Myozunitonirun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it is time for me to play a little game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must attend a conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tristain, Gallia and Germania will try to acquire Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show to that avaricious bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm incompetent, so I shall just sleep and pass time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please summon me any time you need something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do my best to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown tired of Albion already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are certain that Sheffield said there is another wielder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But I have no clue who she was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's as you said, there must be other wielders of the Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania, do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know much about the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has no stone set in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a memento from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saved Saito-san, the stone dissolved and vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power enshrined in this ring shall bring the lost life back to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania, I have no memory of what happened after I was surrounded by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, at that time your heart had stopped beating...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I'll get embarrassed if you all listen so closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't really that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I transported my unconscious partner to Westwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, thank the half-elf girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one who used that magic ring without any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are pretty special,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having such a ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I just did the natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deceased mother used to say that one should help people in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only nature magic can bring the dead back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power is a part of elf magic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that the blood of elves flows in your veins means you can use magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something similar to Void magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't put up any resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We elves do not desire conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone through a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving her alone is the best you can do at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth is such a futile thing in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extravagant banquets...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gardens that please the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Music that pleases the ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all unnecessary in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The music box of the Primogenitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Void wielder must have heard your melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a strange song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I couldn't sleep anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tiffania.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to pronounce, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon I saw from the forest is the\Nsame as the one I see from this balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I drag you into something troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alone since I started living in that little house in the forest four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I'd live alone like that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It was as if we forcefully dragged you out of there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I feel bad about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I wanted to see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to walk freely on this vast world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found that out when my mother passed away\Nand I was about to be taken away by the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why even remembering it is painful for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the magic power I inherited from my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know if it's something good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that either, but it can't be something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some reason that you were\Nborn a half-elf and possess magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how I came here from a distant world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me if you need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who saved my life, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Saito-san. I'm glad to be friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... er... sorry! Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he hate me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the Queen of Tristain, Henrietta,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bestow the title of knight upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you pledge loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Primogenitor, Brimir,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I name you chevalier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now my knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito Chevalier de Hiraga-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Why is Saito your master now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from Her Majesty the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought Siesta-san was appropriate for the position since they get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you for being so considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very grateful as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the formal ceremony is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall prepare dragons to transport you to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must prepare for the conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania will stay here in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is my cousin, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tiffania?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father is my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Archduke of Albion, he governs South Gotha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that we crossed paths must surely be because of Primogenitor Brimir's guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tiffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be lonely in such a big place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with us to the academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. Her Majesty offered that, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I declined her offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't have the resolve to walk among the crowd of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want to be with you, Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd definitely be a burden to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you with everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you sure seem to care about her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you remember that you're my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But protecting fragile maidens is the job of a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chevalier's duty is to assist Her Majesty the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't fight because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can really protect me, then I'll come to the acade{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, we're going back to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the academy as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, Siesta-san, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you made such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Louise will realize that sooner or later as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll warn you since you saved Saito's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do by marching into the academy with such feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to stay in the shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go on like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be many hardships waiting for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but fate will not continue like that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to stand up with your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you got it, stop crying all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And regarding Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't been there, Saito would...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for saying harsh things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito Chevalier de Hiraga-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you return to the academy, you will be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day, Saito Chevalier de Hiraga-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes me kind of nervous. Please call me Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do if you treat me courteously like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, everyone, please take care of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can see the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurrah! Saito Chevalier de Hiraga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurrah! {all the banzais}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're celebrating your elevation to chevalier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The emergency call from the royal palace came early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said to celebrate in as lively a manner as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Majesty insisted on it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't know about the Order of Undine Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we didn't know about it before this morning either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order of Undine Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Reinard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the knightly practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise it'd be a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm blanking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave the complicated details alone for now, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a chevalier changed my opinion of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's all right for me to praise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Majesty is bad at choosing people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, gentlemen of the Order of Undine Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's lift Vice-captain Saito on our\Nshoulders for becoming a chevalier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:35.81,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you are doing to\NHer Highness, Princess Guldenhorf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurrah! The Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurrah! The Undine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and also... Hurrah! Vice-captain Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:55.00,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, and also"? And... vice-captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practicing and practicing every damn day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And ignoring your master and saying you want to protect that half-elf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rumoured Accepted Student.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
